{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/assignment-with-a-returned-value","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Dodela Pomocu Vrucene Return Vrednosti","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kao što pamtiš iz lekcije <a href=\"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/storing-values-with-the-assignment-operator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Čuvanje vrednosti pomoću operatora dodele</a>, sve sa desne strane znaka jednakosti se izračunava pre dodele. To znači da možemo uzeti povratnu vrednost funkcije i dodeliti je promenljivoj.</p>\n<p>Deklarisimo funkciju <code>sum</code> koja sabira dva broja.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">ourSum = sum(5, 12);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Poziv funkcije <code>sum</code> sa argumentima <code>5</code> i <code>12</code> daje return vrednost <code>17</code>. Ta return vrednost se dodeljuje promenljivoj <code>ourSum</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244c3","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Pozovite funkciju <code>processArg</code> sa argumentom <code>7</code> i dodelite njenu return vrednost promenljivoj <code>processed</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16658,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/assignment-with-a-returned-value"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"// Setup\nlet processed = 0;\n\nfunction processArg(num) {\n  return (num + 3) / 5;\n}\n\n// Only change code below this line\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[]